+- [x] GET /healthz - returns ok/stopping/db-failed based on state
+- [x] GET /healthz/** - wildcard alias for health check
+
+## server/ratelimiting - RateLimitStatusController
+- [x] GET /RateLimitingStatus - returns JSON rate limiting status
+
+## server/oauth - TokenKeyEndpoint
+- [x] GET /token_key - returns active signing key (RSA/symmetric, auth-gated)
+- [x] GET /token_keys - returns all signing keys as JWK set
+
+## server/oauth - CheckTokenEndpoint
+- [x] POST /check_token - decodes token, validates scopes (deprecated)
+- [x] GET /check_token - query-string support when allowQueryString=true
+
+## server/oauth - IntrospectEndpoint
+- [x] POST /introspect - RFC-7662 token introspection; returns active flag
+- [x] GET /introspect - returns 405 Method Not Allowed
